      "role": "user",
      "content": "rest? how can i rest when the person everyone thought i was doesn't actually exist? i've spent years building a reputation on a foundation that was basically a hallucination. it feels like i've just been performing a character for everyone. i can't go back to how things were, and i can't move forward because there's nothing to move toward. it's just... empty.",
