      "role": "user",
      "content": "but there is no \"new version\" of me. the version that was capable, the version that had a purpose... that's the only one people cared about. now that's gone. i'm just staring at a blank space where a life used to be. it feels less like a transition and more like a finished chapter. i just don't see how anyone is supposed to keep going when the very thing that gave them meaning is just... evaporated. it's like there's nothing left to do but just stop.",
